% technique v1
! Private and Confidential
& checklist

I. Before school

    1.  Drink first glass of water
    2.  Eat breakfast
    3.  Put dishes into sink
    4.  Get changed
    5.  Drink second glass of water
    6.  Pack school bag
    7.  Clean teeth
    8.  Shoes on, wait by front door!

II. After school

    1.  Shower
    2.  Get changed into home clothes
    3.  Bring lunchbox to kitchen
    4.  Put dirty school clothes at washing machine
    5.  Turn on heater
    6.  Homework (as required)

III. Dinner

    1.  Set table
    2.  Eat dinner
    3.  Put dishes into dishwasher

IV. Bedtime

    1.  Get changed into pyjamas
    2.  Clean teeth
    3.  Into bed!
    4.  Read story
